Scott Stephenson was due to be jailed for stealing a phone from a man dying of hypothermia . 
  He found the man collapsed in the street in South Shields and stole his iPhone 4 instead of calling for help . 
  Stephenson failed to turn up to a previous hearing and was re-bailed for sentence . 
  He shouted and swore outside court after he was bailed for the offence . 
 